{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Doodle Champs is the ultimate party experience for artists and doodlers alike! Play an exciting assortment of doodle-tastic party games with endless replayability, or just draw on a shared online canvas with your pals! Doodle Champs is optimized for play with Wacom tablets, but all pen-wielders and mouse-masters are welcome!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FOUR EXCITING GAME-MODES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/DD1_1.png?t=1736697455\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>On your marks, get set, DRAW!</strong> - Use the Random Prompt Generator to  generate random &amp; hilarious prompts to draw with your friends before time runs out! Then choose from 12 unique medals to award your friends, and see what ridiculous awards your creation received. Before playing again, you can post your creations online or save them straight to your device with or without a background!\u00a0(1-4 players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/MedalsGif.gif?t=1736697455\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DID SOMEBODY SAY...\u00a0<strong>CHAOS MODE!?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While dashing your doodles, keep an eye out for the <strong>CHAOS ORBS</strong>. Click them to summon <strong>Boogers, Bombs, Bird Poop, Bees,</strong> and<strong> THE ALMIGHTY OCTOSQUID</strong> into the game. Mess up your friends' drawings (and maybe even your own!) with the unholy power of <strong><i>CHAOS INK!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/ChaosModeGif.gif?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/CC1_1.png?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No rules, no prompts, no nothin'!</strong> - Enjoy some chill drawing time with ya pals. You and up to three other friends can draw together on a shared, multi-layer online canvas. Collaborate on one special masterpiece, doodle aimlessly while you hang out, or be inspired as you watch your friends' creations come to life before your eyes. (1-4 players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/CC_1.png?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/PP1_1.png?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GET TO WORK!</strong> - Are you a genius inventor? Draw and pitch an exciting new product to solve your client's <i>peculiar problem</i>. After you're assigned one of 80 ludicrous prompts, it's your job to draw a solution and convince your friends to vote to <strong>BUY IT</strong>. But watch out.. If they don't want to BUY IT they might vote for <strong>BOSSMAN</strong> to <strong>FRY IT!!</strong> Whoever earns the most 'DoodleBux' wins the round! - Compete against your friends and come up with the <i>best</i> problem solving inventions. (2-4 players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/FRYITgif.gif?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Take on 20 <i>&quot;cool&quot;</i> clients with over 80\u00a0<i>peculiar</i> problems to solve!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/AA1_1.png?t=1736697455\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ARTISTS ASSEMBLE!</strong> Collaborate as a team to create <strong>the ultimate lifeform!</strong>\u00a0Choose from preset prompts like a Zombie, Robot, Alien, Mermaid, Anime Character - or go promptless and let your friends come up with their own <strong>LIMB-TASTIC</strong> ideas! Each player is randomly assigned a different body part to draw, and when time runs out, your <span class=\"bb_strike\"><strong>monstrosity</strong></span>\u00a0MASTERPIECE is assembled before your eyes! Save your creations to your own private gallery or post them online for all to see. You can also play solo! (1-4 players)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/ArtAssemblyGif1.gif?t=1736697455\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PERSONALISE YOUR GAME!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a range of awesome textured backgrounds to doodle on across all four game modes!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>No microtransactions. No Subscriptions.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/SteamBGgif.gif?t=1736697455\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ACHIEVEMENT HUNTERS WELCOME!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Doodle Champs has over 100  fun achievements to collect across all game modes. <i>Got what it takes to unlock 'em all?</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/extras/SteamCheevos.png?t=1736697455\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736697455","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/page.bg.jpg?t=1736697455","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618320/capsule_231